"Some commands (such as /config, /permissions, /model) open in a full interactive terminal popup sheet, where you can use the interactive CLI interface. The popup closes automatically when the command finishes." = "某些指令（例如 /config、/permissions、/model）會在完整的互動式終端機彈出面板中開啟，你可在其中使用互動式 CLI 介面。指令完成後視窗會自動關閉。";
"Managing Commands" = "管理指令";
"Click the / button in the toolbar, or open Settings → Slash Commands to add, edit, delete, or disable custom commands. Built-in commands can be edited and enabled or disabled in the app." = "點擊工具列中的 / 按鈕，或開啟設定 → 斜線指令，即可新增、編輯、刪除或停用自訂指令。內建指令可在應用程式內編輯內容並啟用或停用。";
"JSON import/export backs up or shares custom commands only. Built-in commands in imported files are ignored." = "JSON 匯入/匯出僅備份或共享自訂指令。匯入檔案中的內建指令將被忽略。";

// File & Image Attachments
