"Type @ in the input field to open a project file search popup. Files are filtered in real time as you type." = "在輸入框中輸入 @ 即可開啟專案檔案搜尋視窗。隨著你的輸入，檔案會即時篩選。";

// Shortcut Buttons
"What are Shortcut Buttons?" = "什麼是快捷按鈕？";
