"Adding a Shortcut" = "新增快捷按鈕";
"Click the ⚡ button in the toolbar to open the Shortcut Manager, or press the + button on the right side of the shortcut bar. You can set a name, message/command, icon, and color." = "點擊工具列中的 ⚡ 按鈕開啟快捷按鈕管理器，或按下快捷按鈕列右側的 + 按鈕。你可以設定名稱、訊息/指令、圖示和顏色。";
"Terminal Command Mode" = "終端機指令模式";
"Enable the \"Run as terminal command\" option to execute the shortcut as a shell command in the inspector terminal instead of sending it as a chat message. The project directory is used as the working directory." = "啟用「作為終端機指令執行」選項後，快捷按鈕將在檢閱器終端機中作為 shell 指令執行，而不是作為對話訊息傳送。專案目錄會被用作工作目錄。";
"Managing Shortcuts" = "管理快捷按鈕";
"Open Settings → Shortcuts to reorder, edit, or delete shortcuts. Shortcut configurations are saved per project." = "開啟設定 → 快捷按鈕，即可重新排序、編輯或刪除快捷按鈕。快捷按鈕設定按專案分別儲存。";
"JSON import/export is supported for backing up or sharing your shortcut set." = "支援透過 JSON 匯入/匯出來備份或共享你的快捷按鈕集合。";

// Inspector Panel
"Opening the Inspector Panel" = "開啟檢閱器面板";
"Click the sidebar.trailing (⊟) button at the top right of the toolbar to toggle the inspector panel. The panel docks to the right side of the window and contains two tabs: Terminal and Memo." = "點擊工具列右上角的 ⊟ 按鈕可展開或收合檢閱器面板。該面板停靠在視窗右側，包含兩個分頁：終端機和備忘。";
"Terminal Tab" = "終端機分頁";
"An embedded zsh terminal that opens at the current project's directory. Use it to run shell commands, inspect files, or manage git — all without leaving the app." = "在目前專案目錄下開啟的內建 zsh 終端機。你可用它執行 shell 指令、檢視檔案或管理 git — 全程無需離開應用程式。";
"Memo Tab" = "備忘分頁";
"A per-project rich text memo editor. Notes are auto-saved after a short pause and persist across sessions. Markdown formatting is supported." = "按專案劃分的富文字備忘編輯器。停頓片刻後備忘會自動儲存，並跨會話保留。支援 Markdown 格式。";
"Heading levels (# / ## / ###)" = "標題等級 (# / ## / ###)";
"Bold" = "粗體";
"Italic" = "斜體";
"Inline code" = "行內程式碼";
"Strikethrough" = "刪除線";
"Unordered list (auto-continues on Return)" = "無序清單（按 Return 時自動延續）";
"Interactive Terminal Popup" = "互動式終端機視窗";
"Some slash commands (such as /config, /permissions, /model) open in a separate interactive terminal sheet. The popup runs the command automatically and closes when it exits." = "某些斜線指令（例如 /config、/permissions、/model）會在獨立的互動式終端機面板中開啟。視窗會自動執行該指令，並在其退出時關閉。";
"The exit code is shown at the bottom — \"exit 0\" means the command completed successfully." = "退出代碼顯示在底部 — 「exit 0」表示指令已成功完成。";

