"Click the GitHub Mark button at the top of the sidebar to open the GitHub panel. After connecting your GitHub account, your repositories are listed and can be added to Clarc with one click." = "點擊側邊欄頂部的 GitHub 標誌按鈕可開啟 GitHub 面板。連接 GitHub 帳戶後，你的儲存庫會列出，並可一鍵新增到 Clarc。";
"Adding a Repository" = "新增儲存庫";
