"Auto-accepts file edits in the working directory (commands still require approval)" = "自動接受工作目錄中的檔案編輯（指令仍需核准）";
"Read-only — analyzes and plans without making edits" = "唯讀 — 在不進行編輯的情況下分析並制定計畫";
"AI auto-approves safe operations, prompts only for risky ones (requires Max/Team/Enterprise/API plan + Sonnet/Opus 4.6+)" = "AI 自動核准安全操作，僅對有風險的操作請求核准（需要 Max/Team/Enterprise/API 方案 + Sonnet/Opus 4.6+）";
