"Skips all permission checks — writes to .git/.vscode/.claude directories still require approval" = "略過所有權限檢查 — 寫入 .git/.vscode/.claude 目錄仍需核准";
"Only enable Skip Permissions on projects you fully trust. Mode changes take effect from the next message." = "僅在你完全信任的專案上啟用。模式變更將從下一則訊息傳送時生效。";
"Double-click" = "按兩下";

"Skip Permissions Mode" = "略過權限模式";
